The paper focuses on face detection in images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of self-supervision and domain adaptation methods also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the research to surgical procedures may also suggest a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM).
